RED FLAGS (Automatic Avoid)
The "Valley Veto": Backmarker + Wide Barrier at Moonee Valley.
The "Fitness Fade": Resuming >150 days without a trial win mentioned.
The "Speed Mirage": Speed Figure >15pts above Class Rating (Apply Cap).
The "Apprentice Risk": Apprentice jockey on a difficult horse (hanging/keen) in a high-pressure race.
